== train2 Â· exercise 2 â€” backward() walks the topo order forward ==
change (in a copy, _ex2.py):  for v in reversed(topo):  ->  for v in topo:

$ python3 _ex2.py --fast
num docs: 488 train / 55 val
vocab size: 38

--- autograd on a graph small enough to check by hand ---
L     data +9.0000 | grad +1.0000
    diff  data -3.0000 | grad -6.0000
        relu  data +2.0000 | grad +0.0000
            sum   data +2.0000 | grad +0.0000
                a*b   data -6.0000 | grad +0.0000
                    a     data +2.0000 | grad +0.0000
                    b     data -3.0000 | grad +0.0000
                const data +8.0000 | grad +0.0000
        const data -5.0000 | grad +0.0000
